Module jbubblebobble.jbubblebobble
Package jbubblebobble.model.level

Class Level

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
jbubblebobble.model.level.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
Observer
public class Level extends Observable implements Observer
Level class is responsible for the level in the game it contains the entities and walls collection and comunicates with the view through the observer pattern
